##Calcul d'un model de regression lineaire simple + calcul du "root mean squared error (RMSE)"

result.msg: Calcul d'un model de regression lineaire simple + calcul du “root mean squared error (RMSE)”

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.mllib.evaluation.RegressionMetrics

val max_sqft_living = training.agg(max(training.col("sqft_living"))).head.getInt(0).toDouble;

val trainingData = training.map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getAs[Integer]("price").toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_living").toDouble / max_sqft_living
    )))

val numIterations = 10
val model = LinearRegressionWithSGD.train(trainingData, numIterations)

model.weights

val testData = test.map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getAs[Integer]("price").toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_living").toDouble / max_sqft_living
    )))

val valuesAndPreds = testData.map { point =>
  val prediction = model.predict(point.features)
  (point.label, prediction)
}

testData.take(10)
trainingData.take(10)
valuesAndPreds.take(10)

val metrics = new RegressionMetrics(valuesAndPreds)
println(s"MSE = ${metrics.meanSquaredError}")
println(s"RMSE = ${metrics.rootMeanSquaredError}")
println(s"R-squared = ${metrics.r2}")
println(s"MAE = ${metrics.meanAbsoluteError}")
println(s"Explained variance = ${metrics.explainedVariance}")

valuesAndPreds.toDF().registerTempTable("valuesAndPreds")
